  <brief_title>Surgery in Treating Patients With Liver Metastasis From a Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumor</brief_title>
  <acronym>GISTs</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase II Multicenter Clinical Trial on Surgery for Patients With Resectable Hepatic Metastasis From Gastrointestinal Stromal Tumors (GISTs)</official_title>
